summary:
Currently I am active as Trainee Marketing EEMEA Distribution at PUMA in Salzburg, Austria. Also, while graduating International Business at The University of Applied Sciences Utrecht (HU) (March 2023).

My previous work experiences include being sales intern EEMEA distribution for PUMA, and working as a manager in a Jumbo store.
